  <brief_title>Congenital Naevi of Lower Limb in the Child</brief_title>
  <acronym>NAEVUS</acronym>
  <official_title>Congenital Nevi in the Lower Limb in Children : Which Size Can be Afforded by a Simple Surgical Procedure ?</official_title>
